paragraphs.title: Unique Article Distribution
paragraphs.text:
%spark
// val uniArticle = wk_merged.filter($"redirect".isNull)
val uniCount = wk_unique.count
val uniRate = rateCal(uniCount, total)

paragraphs.title: Unclosed Structure Distribution
paragraphs.text:
%spark
val unclosed = wk_unique.filter($"unclosed" === true)
val uncloseCount = unclosed.count
val uncloseRate = math.round((uncloseCount / uniCount.toDouble) * 10000) / 10000.0
